Package: libftxui-badwolf-dev
Version: 6.2.0
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: libftxui6.2.0 (= ${binary:Version}), libc6-dev, libstdc++-dev
Description: FTXUI BadWolf — Functional Terminal User Interface library (development files)
 A C++20 library for building rich terminal user interfaces with a
 React-inspired component model, braille charts, GeoJSON maps, and more.
 .
 This package contains the headers and CMake config needed to build
 applications against FTXUI.

Package: libftxui6.2.0
Version: 6.2.0
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FTXUI BadWolf — Functional Terminal User Interface library (runtime)
 A C++20 library for building rich terminal user interfaces with a
 React-inspired component model, braille charts, GeoJSON maps, and more.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries: ftxui-screen, ftxui-dom,
 ftxui-component, and ftxui-ui.

Package: badwolf-tools
Version: 6.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: FTXUI CLI scaffolding tool
 The `ftxui` command-line tool for creating new FTXUI projects,
 listing demos, and scaffolding boilerplate C++ TUI applications.
